industry.name: حمل و نقل، لاجستیک و انبارداری

data.description: Atlantic Ocean Marine & Shipping Services is a Persian licensed freight forwarder that uses people and software to manage the complexity of International trade. Shipping something from Shenzhen to Bandar Abbas or Jebel Ali to LA requires complex coordination. Currently that’s done by telephones, spreadsheets, and fax machines. We provide a web-based app that offers real-time visibility of your shipments.
